               <p>WILLIAM CARTER. I am <rs id="t18260914-130-viclabel768" type="occupation">in service</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-130-victim875 t18260914-130-viclabel768"></join>, in Lower Berkeley-street. On the 7th of July I went to bathe with a friend in the <placeName id="t18260914-130-crimeloc769">Serpentine-river</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18260914-130-crimeloc769" type="placeName" value="Serpentine-river"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18260914-130-crimeloc769" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-130-off766 t18260914-130-crimeloc769"></join>; I met the prisoner near Hyde-park-corner - we all went in together - the prisoner came out first, and, when I came out, he had left the place; I missed my shoes - the prisoner's sold shoes were lying there.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-130-person876">
                  THOMAS 
                  BRACE
               <interp inst="t18260914-130-person876" type="surname" value="BRACE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260914-130-person876" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260914-130-person876" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took up the prisoner in the Park - I told him he had taken a pair of shoes from my friend; he said he had not; I asked him if he would go back to my friend; he said No.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-130-person877">
                  GEORGE 
                  ANDERSON
               <interp inst="t18260914-130-person877" type="surname" value="ANDERSON"></interp>
