                     <interp inst="t18260914-130-person877" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to a shoemaker. The prisoner brought these shoes to my master's shop, about half-past eight or nine o'clock on the 7th of July; I bought them of him.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was in great distress.</p>
